parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I hear something… Is Melissa still in her office?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.If you need to research department files, go to your boss first. Understand?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Yes. Of course. I will talk to Detective Bhatt first thing in the morning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlEx.I would, but it seems our young 1Hero is getting himself into a little trouble.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.You don’t know what you’re talking about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.Kimura doesn't ask for an escort if it isn’t bad. You fucked up this time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m working on a major case. She’s just keeping tabs on me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.If that was true, then why aren’t you allowed in the interrogation room?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoMaOp.I don’t have to listen to this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp^.Someone must have noticed the unauthorized access.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp^.That could have been really bad… She even had Bobby’s squad escort her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp^.There’s no way I can convince Melissa to access the Guild files.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp^.At least I learned that Diana worked for Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp^.Maybe Tasha will give me more if I reveal what I know.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I wonder if David got an alert that I tried to log into his computer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaWoEx.1Hero. Did you see anyone trying to break into my computer?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.You know, I think I did. But I don’t know where they went.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.No sign of the hacker. Plus, it looks like the suspect in the Guild case walked free.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Some days you just have bad luck.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m active. I’m not sitting at my desk all day.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.I ran some checks on the transactions, Miss Bhatt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.Looks like at least one member of the Eclipse Guild had business dealings with Charles Wilkes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaOp.There was a search warrant issued for the mansion in the past…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.How long ago are we talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.That’s all I could find so far.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Come on! The guy was connected to the Guild. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.That doesn’t mean he was murdered. You need some perspective, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.We’re not going to interrogate her over this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I don’t need to interrogate her. I just simply want to have a conversation.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.If anyone is going to talk to her, it will be David.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.I’ve got a lot of work to do. I nominate 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.And just how well do you know her, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Hey, we're both young and attractive. Let me put on the charm.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.As much as you annoy me, you do have a point.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.Trust me. I can get info from her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Okay. Do whatever you need to do. But if you can’t get any information, we’re calling this case closed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaOp.You don’t think there’s some Guild activity going on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.If all the evidence is twenty years old, then we’re not going to waste resources on this case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.There are plenty of fresh leads to follow when it comes to Guild activity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.But if there’s something at the mansion that can tie Lillian to the Guild, I would be interested in that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.When the police searched the mansion, what exactly happened?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.Not sure exactly. But it appears Charles’ lawyers got him off the hook.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.If there’s anything more to it, call me directly. I want to go into this with as much information as possible.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaFlOp.As long as I don’t have to leave the office.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.Are you going to talk to Wilkes’ daughter or not?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEOp.We got trapped in the bunker and had to escape…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.We had to go trekking through a cave to get out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m sure she’ll tell you all about how she figured out an escape route when she comes back to work tomorrow.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Charles was connected to the Guild. He had lots of stolen goods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnEx.That means your girlfriend is connected too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDeNo1.That should be me on the news. I’m the Guild expert.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.You barely know anything about the case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaFlOp.Go catch the raccoon. I hear they are crafty critters… Fast too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Bad hearing too? Maybe it’s time to retire.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaWoCl.Jesus! Glad it’s not me going out there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Shit. I better get moving before it starts raining.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Damn. I better get to the church before the weather gets worse.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.If I’m going to research the Eclipse Guild and find Duncan Helmer, I’m going to need higher security clearance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I can use Melissa’s access code to get to the Eclipse Guild files.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I forgot, I also need her pin to open the files.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Most people around here use their house number…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Melissa lives in the condos near the Channel 4 building…");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.No reason. I just want to know what you’re up to. You’ve got some interesting cases.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.It’s Guild stuff. That’s what the informants are telling me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.It wouldn’t hurt to have a second person in there. Maybe we give it the old good cop, bad cop routine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.If I can just get him to leave the room, I may be able to sneak in there to talk to her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.So you’ve graced us with your presence again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.Ha. At least I get plenty of exercise.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.So why was Kimura asking about me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnEx.Not too sure. When she showed up, she asked who was working the Guild case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.When she found out it was me, she switched to asking where Melissa was.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaDe.I told her Melissa wasn’t back yet after you and her went out to investigate something.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.Then the commissioner asked if you were around instead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.About the Guild case? Why would she want me for that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.Beats me. But hey, you’re a detective. I’m sure you can figure it out if you try.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnEx.Sure thing. I’ll let you know if any other business comes your way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.I’m being sarcastic. Maybe you should hire a secretary.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I wonder what Andrea wants me for.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaAg.Maybe she sees there’s more to me. This could be my big chance to show what I’m capable of!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaDe.But if I don’t talk to her before the day is over, I might miss the opportunity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.First, I’ll have to find her. She’s probably in the executive area upstairs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Hmm. Access to that area is restricted. I wonder how I can get in.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaDe.I don’t know what’s up with Melissa, but I’m not sticking around while she’s in a bad mood.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Make it quick, 1Hero. I have a lot of work to do today.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Madalyn is back in town, and I need to warn Lillian…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.What!? Are you sure? How do you know?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Well… It’s complicated, and I’ve got to run.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.You’re not going to the mansion. You need to focus on your own cases.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.No, it’s not that. I have a meeting with the commissioner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeShOpNo1.What? You scheduled a meeting with Kimura without telling me!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe^.What the hell is going on? Why’s he in so early?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.I’m going to be on the news.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.What are you talking about? The commissioner asked you to be on the news?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I thought she might have told you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.Are you going over my head again, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.She wants me to be on the Guild case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe^.Wait. I’m pretty sure I’m the only one in the office on that case right now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.What did you do, 1Hero? What did you say to her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Nothing… I mean… We just had dinner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.You’re getting distracted. Madalyn Rose is here in North Santiva! I saw her in the forest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Go to your meeting, 1Hero. And don’t do anything stupid.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOP.Mistakes from you reflect poorly on me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.But what about Lillian and Erica? They could be in danger at the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.David, go to the Wilkes’ property, and bring an officer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaShEx^.But, Miss Bhatt, I have work to do today.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Stop being lazy, David. I’ll stop by after my interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe^.I don’t want to babysit a rich kid. I should be doing that interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I better not linger. Andrea is probably waiting for me upstairs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.What the hell am I going to do now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeMaOpNo1.Get your ass in my office! Now!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Just so you know, I was out late last night working on that safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.I told you, let an expert break it open.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Give it to me. We need to get it analyzed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I was supposed to meet with the commissioner, but she didn’t show up this morning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.I’ll take this bottle to the lab to get analyzed and inform the commissioner that a police presence may also be needed at Eve Cathedral.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Fine. I’ll make sure everyone is safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnOp.What the hell are you working on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It’s not our case… It’s an old closed case regarding a dead priest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.But it may be tied to Madalyn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaOp.What the hell are you talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Madalyn is the killer. I just know it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.It’s a hunch. But somehow the Guild, Madalyn, and the dead priest are tied together.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Don’t tell me that you told Andrea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.We’re not keeping secrets from the commissioner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.You don’t need to rub it in… Andrea fired me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.To be honest, I half expected she’d let you off the hook.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnEx.Thanks to you, I have to go to Channel 4 today and do an interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.It was your case to begin with. Shouldn’t you be happy?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.Not if I have to do more work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.What are you going to do now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Clean out my desk… I’m out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.So you’re staying away from the mansion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaAnOp.Come on, detective. You’ve got to leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Fuck! What a thorn in my side!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.People would be a lot less pissed if they would trust me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMaOpNo1.Hey! I’m the only one of us that actually gets anything done!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Fuck! I need to talk to Andrea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnOp.Not sure how you’re going to keep your job after this one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnOp.Not sure how you’re going to keep your job after this one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnOp.How long does she need to be here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Just keep her safe until I come back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.I’m not staying here past my shift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.You tell me. Weren’t you waiting outside the changing room?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.I had work to do, and you looked like you had it under control.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Don’t worry, Judy. This will all be over soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I want you to keep an eye on her. Can you do that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She’s in a bit of trouble and needs to be in a safe place.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.You never leave the office… Just stay here with her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaFlDe.As long as I don’t have to leave the office.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaFlDe.I try my best to keep it clean.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.This place is crawling with cops, Judy. You’ll be safe here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’ll be back before you know it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.Sit down, Miss Judy. And try not to touch the computers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp^.I am very good at being quiet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaFlDe.The best news I’ve heard in the last few minutes.");
